    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to a broad array of equipment that aids the purpose of capturing images photographically, including cameras, darkroom equipment, and any ancillary objects used specifically to capture and process these images.</Note_Text>
